):

1. *Pogodi* ga u glavu! (Hit him in the head!)
2. On *pogodi* kamen u prolazu. (He threw a stone in the passage.)
3. *Pogodila* si pravo mesto. (You guessed the right place.)
4. Ona je *pogodila* da je njena prijateljica tu. (She guessed that her friend was here.)
5. *Pogodio* sam datum za odlazak. (I guessed the date of departure.)
6. *Pogodite* šta se desilo. (Guess what happened.)
7. Da li si *pogodio* šta sam mislio? (Did you guess what I was thinking?)
8. Oni su *pogodili* da će dobiti poklon. (They guessed they would get a gift.)